{"tid":1776442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[台中要人] 台中警暴展招募導覽員志工","createTime":"2019-12-09T14:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T04:56:25.000Z","uid":267429,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3f740638c16f494388184af2342d9370b75975c1","tid":1776442,"uid":267429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:02:03.000Z","msg":"各位好，12月14日-29日會在台中SOGO地下道舉辦香港警暴展。有無手足係台中，可以幫手做當導覽員。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於台灣不少民眾對香港反送中的情況一知半解，甚至無視港警的濫權濫暴而指責示威者，因此各種形式的宣傳都重要(包括目前大家努力在做的連儂墙，街宣，音樂會&hellip;等等)。<br />\n<br />\n辦這次警暴展，是希望揭露港警的濫權、濫暴，抗衡中國的宣傳機器。也藉此讓台灣普羅大眾進一步思索我們能對受到港共、中共政權壓迫之下的被施暴者，提供甚麼樣的幫助？以及借鏡思考身為台灣人在面對中國極權，未來可能會遇到的困境時，我們可以做些甚麼？以此做衍申，加深觀展者護台抗中的意識。<br />\n<br />\n導覽志工需要對香港反修例運動有相當關注，並能向普羅大眾進行解說，台人和港人都歡迎加入。 (12月15日晚上會有一場志工說明會)。<br />\n<br />\n詳情及報名，請點擊志工表格: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1EMn9BA5fSuV85RDEYLIKPCKnhtZ8V4C_wkVB4rRXrso/viewform?edit_requested=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1EMn9BA5fSuV85RDEYLIKPCKnhtZ8V4C_wkVB4rRXrso%2Fviewform%3Fedit_requested%3Dtrue&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2FxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=bac3bebe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1EMn9BA5fSuV85RDEYLIKPCKnhtZ8V4C_wkVB4rRXrso/viewform?edit_requested=true</a>"},{"pid":"e6397b51c236a592ac7053badaf5435e5b9b7f06","tid":1776442,"uid":267429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:10:52.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3571c169d0fe6bfa746a54e754a09f47ad66b41e","tid":1776442,"uid":185490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T20:15:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f499b7e09475be300152cf3f486bdcb56b4702","tid":1776442,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T20:16:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e2b1300c554c2d7b4381a44b1b809da2d5e47f5f","tid":1776442,"uid":75556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T21:03:14.000Z","msg":"薄力一推"},{"pid":"a582541450a46a0dbce1dcefa421f01cbb8d6773","tid":1776442,"uid":343431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T00:25:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42d0a99220278b47f327a98539f3d0c8a192d974","tid":1776442,"uid":267429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:56:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}